EASTERN KENTUCKY HAS MADE BIG

10:14.414 --> 10:16.015
STRIDES IN THE 50 YEARS SINCE

10:16.015 --> 10:17.283
LYNDON JOHNSON CAME THROUGH

10:17.283 --> 10:19.619
HERE, BUT EVEN STILL THE AREA

10:19.619 --> 10:21.921
CONTINUES TO STRUGGLE TODAY.

