THE POVERTY RATE IN EASTERN

10:22.889 --> 10:25.058
KENTUCKY HAS DROPPED, BUT IN

10:25.058 --> 10:27.026
SOME PARTS STILL HOVERS AROUND

10:27.026 --> 10:28.795
30%.

