AND STRAIGHT OUT OF HIGH SCHOOL,

11:10.336 --> 11:12.171
MILLER DID, TOO, WELDING THE

11:12.171 --> 11:13.473
HEAVY MACHINERY USED IN THE

11:13.473 --> 11:14.474
MINES.

