>> YOU JUST CAN'T GO OUT HERE

12:03.056 --> 12:05.491
AND FIND A JOB THAT SUITS YOU.

12:05.491 --> 12:08.061
I MEAN, IT JUST AIN'T HERE.

12:08.061 --> 12:09.295
>> Reporter: SINCE THE 1970s,

12:09.295 --> 12:12.198
MORE THAN 130,000 COAL JOBS HAVE

12:12.198 --> 12:14.100
BEEN LOST IN THE U.S., A DECLINE

