OF ABOUT 50%.

12:16.035 --> 12:17.303
COAL EMPLOYMENT IN EASTERN

12:17.303 --> 12:19.038
KENTUCKY'S NOW AT A HISTORIC

12:19.038 --> 12:20.073
LOW.

12:20.073 --> 12:21.808
MORE THAN 7,000 JOBS HAVE BEEN

12:21.808 --> 12:24.010
LOST SINCE 2008.

12:24.010 --> 12:24.978
>> THE THING THAT HASN'T

12:24.978 --> 12:26.813
HAPPENED AT AN ADEQUATE RATE IS

12:26.813 --> 12:29.148
THE DIVERSIFICATION OF THE LOCAL

12:29.148 --> 12:30.149
ECONOMY.

