>> Reporter: UNIVERSITY OF

12:30.984 --> 12:32.518
KENTUCKY ECONOMIST AND POVERTY

12:32.518 --> 12:34.654
EXPERT JAMES ZILIAK SAYS A

12:34.654 --> 12:36.155
VICIOUS CYCLE IS AT WORK.

