COME AT THIS POINT IN TIME THAT

12:52.405 --> 12:54.507
COAL, IT'S NOT GOING TO BE THE

12:54.507 --> 12:56.209
ENGINE OF JOB GROWTH GOING

12:56.209 --> 12:57.210
FORWARD.

