>> Reporter: THE JOB LOSSES ARE

13:12.825 --> 13:14.460
A HOT TOPIC IN THE SENATE RACE

13:14.460 --> 13:15.128
HERE.

13:15.128 --> 13:16.629
REPUBLICAN INCUMBENT MITCH

13:16.629 --> 13:17.930
McCONNELL HAS TRIED TO

13:17.930 --> 13:19.565
CAPITALIZE ON THE LATEST ROUND

13:19.565 --> 13:21.334
OF ENVIRONMENTAL RULES PROPOSED

13:21.334 --> 13:22.969
BY THE OBAMA ADMINISTRATION LAST

13:22.969 --> 13:23.836
SUMMER.

13:23.836 --> 13:25.238
EVEN DEMOCRATIC CHALLENGER

13:25.238 --> 13:26.973
ALISON LUNDERGAN GRIMES HAS KEPT

13:26.973 --> 13:28.074
HER DISTANCE FROM THE

13:28.074 --> 13:29.142
ADMINISTRATION.

13:29.142 --> 13:30.677
>> I DON'T AGREE WITH WHAT THE

13:30.677 --> 13:32.612
PRESIDENT HAS DONE, HIS ENERGY

13:32.612 --> 13:33.513
PHILOSOPHY.

