KENTUCKY, HE'S ALSO GETTING SOME

13:38.718 --> 13:40.286
CREDIT FOR A NEW PLAN TO BOOST

13:40.286 --> 13:41.954
THE ECONOMY, UNVEILED EARLIER

13:41.954 --> 13:43.022
THIS YEAR.

