>> Reporter: THE PROMISE ZONE

13:48.027 --> 13:49.862
INITIATIVE WILL FIGHT POVERTY BY

13:49.862 --> 13:51.364
CONCENTRATING AID IN SPECIFIC

13:51.364 --> 13:53.366
REGIONS OF THE U.S.

13:53.366 --> 13:55.034
IT'S NOT A NEW IDEA.

13:55.034 --> 13:56.469
REPUBLICAN CONGRESSMAN AND

13:56.469 --> 13:58.204
HOUSING SECRETARY JACK KEMP

13:58.204 --> 14:00.373
PUSHED ENTERPRISE ZONES STARTING

