WHAT IS IT ABOUT THIS PROMISE

14:46.419 --> 14:48.387
ZONE THAT YOU THINK IS GOING TO

14:48.387 --> 14:49.889
ACTUALLY MAKE A DIFFERENCE?

14:49.889 --> 14:50.923
>> I THINK IT GETS BACK TO THE

14:50.923 --> 14:53.226
PARTNERS ALL PULLING TOGETHER.

14:53.226 --> 14:54.227
YOU KNOW, ONE INDIVIDUAL GROUP

14:54.227 --> 14:56.896
CAN ONLY DO SO MUCH, BUT IF YOU

14:56.896 --> 14:58.765
WEAVE US TOGETHER INTO A ROPE,

14:58.765 --> 15:00.333
WE CAN BE REALLY, REALLY STRONG.

15:00.333 --> 15:01.434
>> THE PEOPLE OF THE REGION HAVE

15:01.434 --> 15:02.335
SAID, THIS IS IT.

15:02.335 --> 15:04.971
WE'VE GOT TO DO SOMETHING NOW OR

15:04.971 --> 15:07.607
ELSE WE MIGHT NOT BE ABLE TO

15:07.607 --> 15:08.608
PULL BACK.

15:08.608 --> 15:09.308
>> Reporter: IN FACT, THE

15:09.308 --> 15:10.343
PROMISE ZONE HAS BROUGHT

15:10.343 --> 15:11.778
TOGETHER A NEW COALITION OF

15:11.778 --> 15:13.880
LOCAL GOVERNMENTS, SCHOOLS AND

15:13.880 --> 15:15.348
COMMUNITY ORGANIZATIONS THAT

15:15.348 --> 15:16.749
WILL IMPLEMENT THE PROMISE ZONE

15:16.749 --> 15:19.418
GOALS: DIVERSIFYING THE ECONOMY,

15:19.418 --> 15:21.420
CREATING JOBS, GROWING SMALL

15:21.420 --> 15:22.989
BUSINESS, AND IMPROVING

15:22.989 --> 15:25.091
EDUCATION AND RETRAINING.

