THE WORK IS JUST GETTING UNDER

15:26.159 --> 15:27.760
WAY, BUT RICKETT POINTS TO A

15:27.760 --> 15:29.028
COUPLE SUCCESSFUL LOCAL

15:29.028 --> 15:30.630
INITIATIVES THAT SHOW HOW THE

15:30.630 --> 15:32.165
PROMISE ZONE COULD WORK.

15:32.165 --> 15:33.766
>> WE'VE GOT TO GET A BETTER-

15:33.766 --> 15:36.235
EDUCATED WORKFORCE, GOT TO HELP

15:36.235 --> 15:38.137
THE ADULTS THAT, YOU KNOW, NEED

15:38.137 --> 15:39.572
ADDITIONAL TRAINING OR

15:39.572 --> 15:41.674
RETRAINING.

15:41.674 --> 15:42.608
>> Reporter: ESPECIALLY

15:42.608 --> 15:44.177
UNEMPLOYED COAL MINERS.

15:44.177 --> 15:45.444
MANY ARE LEAVING IN DROVES TO

15:45.444 --> 15:46.579
FIND WORK.

