AT HIS NEARBY COMMUNITY COLLEGE,

16:07.533 --> 16:08.968
HE'S EARNING AN ASSOCIATE'S

16:08.968 --> 16:10.469
DEGREE TO REPAIR HEATING, AIR

16:10.469 --> 16:12.004
CONDITIONING AND VENTILATION

16:12.004 --> 16:14.574
SYSTEMS, OR H.V.A.C.

