>> WE REALLY BELIEVE IN

16:33.793 --> 16:35.261
ENTREPRENEURSHIP, TRYING TO GET

16:35.261 --> 16:37.330
BUSINESSES TO START, TRYING TO

16:37.330 --> 16:38.531
FIND WAYS TO HELP THE ONES THAT

16:38.531 --> 16:40.833
ARE HERE, YOU KNOW, THRIVE.

